Package complexity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Method
    Implementations of this class should have names suggesting a particular complexity class, and should implement the method and complexity methods in a way that corresponds to the class name.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Linear
    A linear implementation of Method.
    Tester
    This class provides a facility for timing execution of a Timer's method, for increasing values of method's parameter (modelling the "size of the problem"), terminating the test sequence when a maximum execution time is exceeded.
    Timer
    Adds a timer functionality to Method objects.
